### Better Auth Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/ok

### Test Current Session (should return 401 if not authenticated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me

### Test Protected Route (should return 401 if not authenticated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/protected

### Test Public Route (accessible without auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/public

### Sign Up New User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/sign-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Sign In User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: localhost:3000

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

### Get Session After Sign In (use the session cookie from sign-in response)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/me

### Test Protected Route After Sign In
GET http://localhost:3000/api/protected

### Sign Out User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/sign-out

### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tasks

### Create New Task (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn Prisma with Better Auth",
  "description": "Implement CRUD operations using Prisma and Better Auth"
}

### Update Task (requires authentication)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Task Title",
  "completed": true
}

### Delete Task (requires authentication)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
